org.phoenixbioinformatics.api.db.api

Class AbstractSubscriptionTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractDto
      • org.phoenixbioinformatics.api.db.api.AbstractSubscriptionTransaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto, com.poesys.db.dto.IObserver, com.poesys.db.dto.ISubject, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto>, ISubscriptionTransaction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SubscriptionTransaction

    public abstract class AbstractSubscriptionTransaction
extends com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractDto
implements ISubscriptionTransaction

    A data-access layer data-transfer object for the SubscriptionTransaction. This class is an abstract class that contains AndroMDA generated code; change nothing in this class. Instead, override any methods in the concrete subclass generated in the same package. AndroMDA will overwrite this class each time you run it but will never overwrite the concrete subclass.

    A specific transaction related to the subscription; provides the transactional history for the subscription

    Stereotypes:

    • CompositeKey
    • Persistent

    Class is read/write: true

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
    See Also:
